t() 方法用以在鼠标事件创建时 (一般用 Document.createEvent()方法创建) 初始化其属性的值。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MouseEvent.initMouseEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"event.initMouseEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"MouseEvent.initMouseEvent()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"event.initMouseEvent","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/mouseevent/initmouseevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/mouseevent/initmouseevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent","title":"鼠标事件"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/initMouseEvent","title":"MouseEvent.initMouseEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"MouseEvent.initMouseEvent() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}